	<AE_Replicator.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.2.AnomalyLabel>复制者</AE_Replicator.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.2.AnomalyLabel>
    <!-- EN: A white-colored figure made of clay-like material. Can make more of itself -->
